{"tid":1439566,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 對藍絲應該點做？","createTime":"2019-08-10T06:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T13:04:44.000Z","uid":304170,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c3eaef3c45da11b77dc71ce7d7a4d2db9e6e9c4","tid":1439566,"uid":304170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"面對藍絲，和理非成日都想以理服人，講解政府依樣唔啱嗰樣黐撚線。但完全不能動搖佢地信念，點解？<br />\n<br />\n其實好可能係因為佢地信奉<span style=\"color: red;\">權威主義</span> (Authoritarianism)，佢地通常好鍾意以下的三樣嘢：<br />\n1. 保守主義（Conventionalism）─ 對於<span style=\"color: red;\">傳統社會規範</span>及中產階級價值的墨守成規；<br />\n2. 權威性的服從（Authoritarian submission）─ 對於團體內的<span style=\"color: red;\">權威</span>採取被動的服從及非批判性的態度；<br />\n3. 權威性的強加（Authoritarian aggression）─ 傾向對於<span style=\"color: red;\">傳統規範及價值</span>不服從者採取譴責、排擠與懲罰；<br />\n<br />\n鍾意呢三樣嘢嘅幾乎都會<br />\n* 有民族優越感 (ethnocentrism)<br />\n* 不容許相反的政治主張 (political intolerance)<br />\n* 反民主 (anti-democratic)<br />\n<br />\n當中「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">權威性的強加</span>」最有決定性。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">reference:<br />\nDunwoody, P. T., &amp; Funke, F. (2016). The aggression-submission-conventionalism scale: Testing a new three factor measure of authoritarianism. Journal of Social and Political Psychology, 4(2), 571&ndash;600. doi:10.5964/jspp.v4i2.168 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.psycharchives.org/bitstream/20.500.12034/1416/1/jspp.v4i2.168.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psycharchives.org%2Fbitstream%2F20.500.12034%2F1416%2F1%2Fjspp.v4i2.168.pdf&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s2Ckd6W2E%2BSZ990UparCCSw%3D&h=42aac1f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.psycharchives.org/bitstream/20.500.12034/1416/1/jspp.v4i2.168.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://whogovernstw.org/2014/10/03/kuanweiwu1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwhogovernstw.org%2F2014%2F10%2F03%2Fkuanweiwu1%2F&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s2Ckd6W2E%2BSZ990UparCCSw%3D&h=44b94b82\" target=\"_blank\">https://whogovernstw.org/2014/10/03/kuanweiwu1/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n非常可惜，信奉權威主義嘅堅定似乎是<span style=\"color: red;\">天生</span>的，高學歷者尤其堅定。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">reference:<br />\nLudeke SG, Krueger RF (2013) Authoritarianism as a personality trait: evidence from a longitudinal behavior genetic study. Personal Individ Differ 55:480484 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0191886913001827\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0191886913001827&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s2Ckd6W2E%2BSZ990UparCCSw%3D&h=d051095b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0191886913001827</a></span><br />\n<br />\n要徹底改變佢地應該無可能，只能儘量拉佢地番比較中間嘅位置，所以我地要對依啲人繼續講清事實，並<br />\n1. 詮釋政府做緊嘅嘢為&ldquo;非傳統規範&ldquo;<br />\n    * 獨立調查委員會並不罕見<br />\n    * 廿三條是撤回的，三隧分流是撤回的<br />\n    * 不聽勸諫非「明君」所為<br />\n2. 詮釋我地爭取緊嘅嘢為&ldquo;傳統價值&ldquo;<br />\n    * 抗爭自古以來經常發生<br />\n3. 矮化固有權威<br />\n    * 宣揚政府無道義，講大話，例如低收入人士勞工問題遲遲不解決。能力低，派四千蚊都搞幾年<br />\n4. 淡化從屬關係<br />\n    * 解釋政府應服務市民，而非市民服從政府。例如說，稅是市民交的<br />\n<br />\n至於實質點做？<br />\ner... 我唔知啊<br />\n<br />\n純粹拋磚引玉，集思廣益。"},{"pid":"7ee51f64f913089780dc112c25a120592c11183b","tid":1439566,"uid":304170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:19:02.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"29a747b0e124d38e057e016e2d6d0d2ac3160cda","tid":1439566,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:28:15.000Z","msg":"比佢更藍<br />\n宣傳信用系統"},{"pid":"5bc5c40c92c1c80b8addc27af4e9bcba7c0ce74c","tid":1439566,"uid":304170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"29a747b0e124d38e057e016e2d6d0d2ac3160cda","tid":1439566,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:28:15.000Z","msg":"比佢更藍<br />\n宣傳信用系統"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T09:35:03.000Z","msg":"有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f96986adb02