 />"},{"pid":"822c21042d87e1b86335a3e3e64575c40fae55d4","tid":1439566,"uid":304788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:49:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d602c0b33bcb6cd22ba2e8888015afcff738a190","tid":1439566,"uid":253573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:49:45.000Z","msg":"文宣要試下其他方向 要大大力咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續放映會<br />\n派傳單<br />\n郵寄文宣資料去你附近既大廈 低成本就逼到唔同立場既人拆開黎睇<br />\n文宣圖要集中請有用資訊 唔係得個靚<br />\n同豬要講飼料講民生"},{"pid":"8a49041d2e8c0ac6d447c632d9c7953ef76dbf3b","tid":1439566,"uid":304170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:01:30.000Z","msg":"佢哋心底好想做「正常人」，所以我哋要將和平示威成為日常事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f6199d4acf507c6da6f5579558c7f4b769a621","tid":1439566,"uid":304788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:42:36.000Z","msg":"林奠講no stake in the society都係繼續有關權威性嘅套路。我地要講翻大把有事業嘅人喺同一陣線<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5130e0699048a3d1c62194ae4085f1e54ffa47b7","tid":1439566,"uid":304788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:03:18.000Z","msg":"其實藍絲好純真，要佢地支持可能比想像中易<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438639</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"213b780aeb4a5a8a7179f429bcea9fd5c59d6265","tid":1439566,"uid":77220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:07:29.000Z","msg":"要反屋企紅底要變得比佢地更紅<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1278154\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1278154</a>"},{"pid":"15bcdf71d22163087065152f37f64a5dce85c3ac","tid":1439566,"uid":77220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:08:33.000Z","msg":"比紅更紅，比藍更藍。藍撚到佢驚！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/14